snippet.title: Communite: Build Together - Official Beta Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description: Here's your look at Communite: Build Together in this trailer for the upcoming multiplayer city builder game. Check out the trailer to learn about your objectives as you and your friends build a cozy world, rescue NPC friends, and more. Communite: Build Together is currently in early Beta, and it will be available on Steam and Google Play.
